testing 58 fire pet it casts VERY often.<br>
<br>
SELF BUFFS<br>
Shieldskin  (55 hp rune)<br>
Shielding (ac 14, hp 50 MR 12) this is new?<br>
O'Kiels embers<br>
<br>
ON OTHERS (3 new)<br>
Force Shock (as before 179 hp DD pushback)<br>
Tishan's Clash (50 hp 5 sec stun, pet casts this a ton!)<br>
Garrions Mighty Mana Shock (148 hp dd)<br>
Enstill (96 sec)<br>
Cancel Magic (blech)<br>
<br>
52 Fire seems to cast similarly less tests with it though.<br>
